- Let's go.

544
00:37:05,464 --> 00:37:08,730
I will brief you about today's work.

545
00:37:12,543 --> 00:37:14,078
- Ouch!
- Be careful.

546
00:37:14,078 --> 00:37:16,922
Guys, be careful of your heads.

547
00:37:16,922 --> 00:37:18,690
Is this the place?

548
00:37:20,968 --> 00:37:22,828
We are going to pick up the trash.

549
00:37:22,828 --> 00:37:25,898
