570
00:38:30,669 --> 00:38:32,981
There's so much to work on.

571
00:38:34,074 --> 00:38:35,384
There's so much trash to pick up.

572
00:38:35,384 --> 00:38:38,404
I will carry the heavier ones.

573
00:38:38,404 --> 00:38:40,631
