- Aigoo.

580
00:38:57,834 --> 00:39:00,033
One, two, three!

581
00:39:03,144 --> 00:39:06,806
What the—... Since when did those two become so close?

582
00:39:12,264 --> 00:39:15,623
Snake! Snake! Snake! Shit!

583
00:39:18,713 --> 00:39:21,754
This is just a rubber hose!

584
00:39:25,464 --> 00:39:26,827
Hold my hand.

585
00:39:31,974 --> 00:39:34,008
Aigoo.

586
00:39:46,524 --> 00:39:47,714
It's hot! Hot!

587
00:39:47,714 --> 00:39:49,764
Careful.

588
00:39:49,764 --> 00:39:51,414
Wow!

589
00:39:52,474 --> 00:39:55,734
- How is it? Is it fine?
- It's good.

590
00:39:55,734 --> 00:39:58,592
Thank you for your hard work today.

591
00:39:58,592 --> 00:40:01,152
No problem. It was so much fun.

592
00:40:05,174 --> 00:40:07,871
Hyung Jin Wook, why aren't you drinking?

593
00:40:07,871 --> 00:40:10,941
Oh, because I don't want to lose my muscle mass.

594
00:40:10,941 --> 00:40:12,905
I feel the same.

595
00:40:12,905 --> 00:40:15,334
Jay, are you okay after that fall earlier?

596
00:40:15,334 --> 00:40:17,402
Yes, I'm okay.

597
00:40:18,684 --> 00:40:20,439
Did you wash yourself off properly?

598
00:40:20,439 --> 00:40:22,116
I'm not sure.

599
00:40:22,116 --> 00:40:24,435
Things are still stuck on you.

600
00:40:24,435 --> 00:40:25,828
Aigoo.

601
00:40:25,828 --> 00:40:27,910
<i>Is it because I drank too much?</i>

602
00:40:27,910 --> 00:40:30,260
