603
00:40:31,964 --> 00:40:35,261
I will go and get ready to sleep.

604
00:40:48,092 --> 00:40:49,676
Let's clean up together in the morning.

605
00:40:49,676 --> 00:40:51,763
I will just clean up and go to bed.

606
00:40:51,763 --> 00:40:54,689
- Then I'll go to bed first, okay?
- Yes, go ahead.

607
00:41:21,083 --> 00:41:22,451
Hey!

608
00:41:27,257 --> 00:41:29,145
Where are you going?

609
00:41:29,145 --> 00:41:31,263
Nothing. I was just...

610
00:41:31,263 --> 00:41:34,248
Do you like him that much that you sneak after him?

611
00:41:34,248 --> 00:41:36,143
What are you talking about?

612
00:41:36,143 --> 00:41:38,187
Speaking to him every day isn't enough.

613
00:41:38,187 --> 00:41:40,022
You even follow him to volunteer work.

614
00:41:40,022 --> 00:41:43,441
Do you really just like him as an older brother?

615
00:41:46,271 --> 00:41:48,447
Hey! Don't be silent.

616
00:41:48,447 --> 00:41:50,366
