617
00:41:50,366 --> 00:41:51,975
I do have feelings.

618
00:41:53,911 --> 00:41:55,487
What?

619
00:41:58,983 --> 00:42:00,842
I do have feelings.

620
00:42:02,537 --> 00:42:04,287
So it is true.

621
00:42:04,905 --> 00:42:06,948
Jay...

622
00:42:06,948 --> 00:42:08,683
I have feelings for you.

623
00:42:47,749 --> 00:42:50,207
Hyung, what are you doing here?

624
00:42:50,807 --> 00:42:52,130
Oh!

625
00:42:52,684 --> 00:42:56,529
I couldn't finish organizing this morning. I was doing the rest.

626
00:42:56,529 --> 00:42:59,157
I will help.

627
00:42:59,157 --> 00:43:03,694
Okay. Why are you awake at this hour, though?

628
00:43:04,378 --> 00:43:07,123
I just couldn't get to sleep.

629
00:43:07,123 --> 00:43:08,891
Is that so?

630
00:43:25,496 --> 00:43:27,289
<i>I do have feelings.</i>

631
00:43:27,289 --> 00:43:28,832
<i>Jay, I have feelings for you.</i>

632
00:43:28,832 --> 00:43:30,009
<i>Did I hear that right?</i>

633
00:43:30,009 --> 00:43:32,635
<i>I didn't hear it incorrectly, did I?</i>

634
00:43:39,813 --> 00:43:41,558
<i>Let's calm down.</i>

635
00:43:41,558 --> 00:43:46,476
<i>But... why is it me and not Hyung Jin Wook?</i>

636
00:44:27,308 --> 00:44:29,675
Jay, did you sleep well?

637
00:44:29,675 --> 00:44:31,009
Yes, I did.

638
00:44:31,009 --> 00:44:33,198
Let's pack up and leave.

639
00:44:33,968 --> 00:44:37,399
Guys, wake up! Wake up.

640
00:44:42,500 --> 00:44:44,986
Hey, was the ramyeon I made yesterday tasty?

641
00:44:44,986 --> 00:44:47,572
I liked Oppa's* ramyeon more.
<i>("older brother," used by Korean females)</i>

642
00:44:47,572 --> 00:44:50,415
- Let's come here again next time.
- Yes, that sounds great!

643
00:44:50,415 --> 00:44:53,454
