644
00:44:53,454 --> 00:44:55,556
I'm sure everyone is quite exhausted.

645
00:44:55,556 --> 00:44:59,435
I want to get home early, skip any distractions, wash up, and go to bed.

646
00:44:59,435 --> 00:45:01,380
Guys, say goodbye.

647
00:45:01,380 --> 00:45:03,981
<i>Bye!</i>

648
00:45:14,286 --> 00:45:16,196
<i>[You two look so good together! More videos of you two, please!]</i>

649
00:45:16,196 --> 00:45:18,386
<i>[Two handsome boys together, so cute!]</i>

650
00:45:18,386 --> 00:45:20,286
<i>[I hope you two film the next video!]</i>

651
00:45:20,286 --> 00:45:21,314
Okay!

652
00:45:21,314 --> 00:45:24,986
