663
00:45:52,429 --> 00:45:55,133
Sounds good! Have you ever made any healthy meals?

664
00:45:55,133 --> 00:45:59,286
No, my mom cooks everything for me.

665
00:46:00,086 --> 00:46:03,039
What will be a good menu idea?

666
00:46:03,039 --> 00:46:06,253
Oh, I should ask Hyung Jin Wook about it!

667
00:46:06,253 --> 00:46:09,171
Oh, that sounds good.

668
00:46:09,171 --> 00:46:10,723
Ask him and let me know.

669
00:46:10,723 --> 00:46:12,232
I will.

670
00:46:14,736 --> 00:46:18,373
