673
00:46:23,794 --> 00:46:25,826
I have some photos. Do you want to see?

674
00:46:25,826 --> 00:46:27,336
Yes, please.

675
00:46:30,816 --> 00:46:32,520
There are so many!

676
00:46:33,046 --> 00:46:37,517
So many! I've never thought about healthy recipes, but there are so many!

677
00:46:39,026 --> 00:46:41,016
You two seem to be having fun.

678
00:46:41,016 --> 00:46:43,016
