679
00:46:43,016 --> 00:46:46,917
I was showing Jay some healthy meals that I've made.

680
00:46:46,917 --> 00:46:48,790
Do you want to see them too?

681
00:46:51,196 --> 00:46:54,392
<i>I do have feelings. Jay, I have feelings for you.</i>

682
00:46:54,392 --> 00:46:57,344
<i>Why does that moment keep popping into my head?</i>

683
00:46:57,344 --> 00:46:59,931
