694
00:47:29,754 --> 00:47:31,885
- See you later.
- Okay.

695
00:47:32,696 --> 00:47:34,006
See you later.

696
00:47:34,006 --> 00:47:36,016
Wait for me!

697
00:47:36,906 --> 00:47:40,079
I need to shop for ingredients. Let's go to the gym tomorrow.

698
00:47:40,079 --> 00:47:42,204
Yes, fine.

