00:47:57,186 --> 00:47:59,031
- Ji Won.
- Yes, Oppa?

700
00:47:59,031 --> 00:48:02,309
Come over as soon your work is done, okay?

701
00:48:02,309 --> 00:48:04,979
Okay, Oppa. By the way, you look really excited.

702
00:48:04,979 --> 00:48:06,939
You know, I'm a good cook.

703
00:48:06,939 --> 00:48:09,373
- I'm heading out.
- Okay. See you later!

