724
00:49:29,076 --> 00:49:31,206
Where was it?

725
00:49:31,206 --> 00:49:33,150
Jay!

726
00:49:35,536 --> 00:49:37,836
Jay!

727
00:49:37,836 --> 00:49:40,233
Yes? What is it?

728
00:49:41,046 --> 00:49:42,634
What's going on?

729
00:49:42,634 --> 00:49:44,352
Why are you guys here?

730
00:49:47,506 --> 00:49:50,266
I thought about it...

